title: First choice
text: Correct: Great job! In this case, you are a data producer because you produced the calculated fields on your report.

title: Second choice
text: Incorrect: Not quite. As the data consumer, it is critical that you flag data quality issues to your colleagues in the data team but you are not the producer of data in the source. Because of that reason you are not responsible for remediating issues.

title: Third Choice
text: Incorrect: The data quality team monitors data quality dashboards to hold parties accountable for remediating data quality issues
